<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/616255-i-read-this-book-but-i-m-still-a-little">I read this book but I&#39;m still a little confused about what&#39;s true and what&#39;s not. I understand that there was some sort of scandal because Shin was not entirely truthful about his story at first. But is everything in this book true? I&#39;d ahte to think I read something that&#39;s not.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_616255'><a id="like_count_community_question_616255" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/616255?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13604229-escape-from-camp-14">like</a></span>

