<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link148904" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=148904&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F334229-i-can-understand-why-china-and-south-korea%2Fanswers%2F148904-nobody-know-how-north">flag</a>
